## How to Run

```bash
# 1 â€” Start PostgreSQL (Docker Compose or local)
docker compose up -d db

# 2 â€” Start backend (auto-seeds DB on first run)
cd VMS
./mvnw spring-boot:run

# 3 â€” Start frontend
cd VMS-Frontend.PleaseWork/Ye/VMS-Frontend.Vue/VMS-Frontend
npm run dev
```

Then open `http://localhost:5173` â€” you'll be redirected to `/login`.

> [!NOTE]
> The backend runs on port **8081**. Make sure `VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8081` is set in the frontend `.env` file (or the fallback in [http.js](file:///c:/Users/msi/Desktop/MyWorkspace/VMS-Complete/VMS-Frontend.PleaseWork/Ye/VMS-Frontend.Vue/VMS-Frontend/src/lib/http.js) is used automatically).

